  <brief_title>Early Outcome Assessment of Revision Total Knee Arthroplasty Using Metaphyseal Sleeves</brief_title>
  <official_title>Early Outcome Assessment of Revision Total Knee Arthroplasty Using Metaphyseal Sleeves</official_title>
